{"tid":2188615,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"冚賭檔被捕 兩警一起訴一放生","createTime":"2020-09-04T10:52:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T10:56:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0c20febf257a807ae04d7331a765a7c4985d0554","tid":2188615,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T10:52:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200904/76K55DTATNGJBOVPPLIFRWBYRU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200904%2F76K55DTATNGJBOVPPLIFRWBYRU%2F&d=HMiOmB7b1AqxO%2BCwCPl1ccvW%2Fvk9QtnWk1JKGKfj%2Fbg%3D&h=b719f8b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200904%2F76K55DTATNGJBOVPPLIFRWBYRU%2F&h=a408fe30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200904/76K55DTATNGJBOVPPLIFRWBYRU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n冚賭檔被捕 兩警一起訴一放生<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Xzzp2RgwP3DBo1bRnvU7zU9VgqY=/1810x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QBYEERYXOFCBTPVWONOT3A3CE4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FXzzp2RgwP3DBo1bRnvU7zU9VgqY%3D%2F1810x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQBYEERYXOFCBTPVWONOT3A3CE4.jpg&h=6e81519d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■涉事賭檔位於屯門一幢工廈，以Party Room掩飾。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警察知法犯法事件停不了！今年5月警方在屯門搗破一個非法賭博場所並拘捕36人，揭發案中有案，其中兩名被捕男子竟是休班警。經四個月調查，警方昨落案起訴其中一名涉案警員一項協助管理賭場罪，案件今日提堂；另一名涉案警員則無條件獲釋。<br />\n<br />\n近月在武漢肺炎疫情下，警方屢破工廈非法賭檔，今次涉案被控警員的案件於今年5月4日發生，當晚約11時15分警方突擊。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被控協助管理賭場今提堂<br />\n<br />\n至於被捕兩警，53歲姓潘休班警為屯門警區軍裝警員，平日嗜賭成性，欠債纍纍；另一名被捕的33歲姓陳休班警則隸屬大埔警區刑事調查隊，二人事後已被停職。<br />\n<br />\n事隔四個月，警方昨落案控告潘一項協助管理賭場罪，。。。"},{"pid":"2cd87e01dfb6632581a423bb2ff650fecf9bb86b","tid":2188615,"uid":187232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T10:56:13.000Z","msg":"係咪轉做污點證人啊，賤狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}